pip install poetry
pip install black
poetry init   > em Dependencias instale o pytest e factory-boy / ou poetry add pytest / poetry add factory-boy
poetry add django
poetry run django-admin startproject bookstore .
poetry run python manage.py startapp api
poetry run python manage.py migrate
poetry run python manage.py runserver
poetry add djangorestframework
poetry update

>no arquivo settings.py adicione 'rest_framework' em INSTALLED_APPS
